snippet.title: NEW OTOME - Garden of Seif: Curse of Gravehollow Peaks Official Trailer 2022
snippet.description:
Lost in the cursed mountains of Gravehollow Peaks, two rival assassins must set their differences aside and find a way home... unless something finds them first. A story-rich fantasy with magic, romance, and choices that matter. 

WISHLIST: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2079430/Garden_of_Seif_Curse_of_Gravehollow_Peaks/
FOLLOW US: https://foxdriftstudios.carrd.co/

Garden of Seif: Curse of Gravehollow Peaks is an alternate side story based on the upcoming game Garden of Seif: Chronicles of an Assassin. Follow the main story on Kickstarter 

KICKSTARTER: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/garden-of-seif/garden-of-seif-chronicles-of-an-assassin
